  20 Oct 2006; Bryan Østergaard <kloeri@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on Alpha.

  30 Aug 2006; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.5.ebuild,
  vls-0.5.5-r1.ebuild, vls-0.5.6-r1.ebuild, vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  Set HOMEPAGE to the correct page, solving Bug #145390.

  20 May 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/vls-0.5.6-64bit.patch, files/vls-0.5.6-dvdread.patch,
  +files/vls-0.5.6-gmake-3.81.patch, vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  Add patch to fix building with GCC 4.1.1 on 64-bit platforms, add patch to
  fix building with gmake 3.81 (bug #132952), and fix patch to build with
  newer dvdread versions.

  17 Apr 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/vls-0.5.6-dvdread.patch, vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  Add patch to build with latest libdvdread, bug #128840.

  18 Mar 2006; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.5-r1.ebuild,
  vls-0.5.6-r1.ebuild, vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  Cleaned up dvb-dependencies

  01 Mar 2006; Patrick McLean <chutzpah@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  Add ~amd64.

  22 Feb 2006; Joshua Jackson <tsunam@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on x86; bug #123599

  03 Nov 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.5.ebuild,
  vls-0.5.5-r1.ebuild, vls-0.5.6-r1.ebuild, vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
