  02 Sep 2005; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.6-r1.ebuild,
  vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
  added include path for newer libdvb ebuild

  19 Jun 2005; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> vls-0.5.6-r2.ebuild:
